I don't see kvmppc_get_tb_offset_hv in this patch.

> diff --git a/arch/powerpc/kvm/book3s_64_mmu_hv.c b/arch/powerpc/kvm/book3=
s_64_mmu_hv.c
> index 7f765d5ad436..738f2ecbe9b9 100644
